{"tid":1876534,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"★深水埗地舖獲茶餐廳租客洽租 月租16.5萬港元","createTime":"2020-02-12T12:38:13.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-13T03:53:06.000Z","uid":19454,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"8a86cf69a3cb9a3105fabee9138a1f48068eebad","tid":1876534,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-12T12:38:13.000Z","msg":"中原商舖部張嘉偉表示，深水埗汝州街210至214號地下，地舖面積約2,370方呎，另有約1,515方呎入則閣，總面積約3,885方呎，獲茶餐廳承租，成交月租約16.5萬港元，平均呎租約42元。<br />\n<br />\n該舖位前租客為中信銀行，舊租金約22.4萬元，於去年遷出後，業主隨即將物業放租，意向月租約20萬元，惟去年中爆發社會運動，招租反應一般，經數月後，終獲茶餐廳租客洽租，業主有感準租客具誠意，加上為免物業持續丟空，故接受大幅議價，最終成功租出，新租金較舊租大跌約26%<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/finance/20200212/bkn-20200212174916790-0212_00842_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Ffinance%2F20200212%2Fbkn-20200212174916790-0212_00842_001.html&d=DYxn%2BwEapY32uLV96Ej4GKjoMSgg1pB26AL%2BN7DPQls%3D&h=2cfa94ee\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/finance/20200212/bkn-20200212174916790-0212_00842_001.html</a>"},{"pid":"eb554985a66b662dd6f76e5c9b0d4917f3d67832","tid":1876534,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-12T12:38:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b423b795640af9ad7288274093ec48cd86d2d040","tid":1876534,"uid":19454,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-12T12:39:42.000Z","msg":"可能想搞 <span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">茶記家族</span>"},{"pid":"44d96330630ae248d0f4742bc86ea04cfde10991","tid":1876534,"uid"